Ye Pattern Actually Karta Kya Hai?
Ye input ko 3 steps me handle karta hai:

1.Grammar define karta hai
Matlab: kya allowed hai =  numbers , operators (+, -, AND, OR) , variables

2.Expression Tree banata hai
String ko directly run nahi karta
👉 usko tod ke objects banata hai
5 + 3 - 2
      (-)
     /   \
   (+)    2
  /   \
 5     3


 3.Har node khud ko evaluate karta hai
 Har class ke paas ek method hota hai: = interpret()
 Aur wo apna result return karta hai.


 Flow kaise chalta hai (step-by-step)
 Step 1: Input aaya
 Step 2: Parse hua (manual ya parser se)
 Objects bane:
 Number(5)
 Number(3)
 Add(...)
 Subtract(...)

 Step 3: Tree bana
 Step 4: Evaluation
 Add → 5 + 3 = 8
 Subtract → 8 - 2 = 6
 👉 Final result: 6


